## 🛠️ How to Run This Project
1. Open **Swift Playgrounds** on your iPad or Mac (or open **Xcode**).
2. Create a new App project.
3. Replace the code inside your `ContentView.swift` file with the fundamental SwiftUI code from this repository.
4. Click the Run button to test it instantly in the live interactive simulator pane.
